      a.button(href="#") Explore All
    footer.footer
      .container.footer-container
        .footer-top
          .footer-columns
            .footer-column
              a.footer-logo(href="/")
                img(srcSet="./images/logo.png 2x")
              p.footer-desc Similarly, a loan taken out to buy a car may be secured by the car. The duration of the loan.
              form.subcribe
                input(type="email" placeholder="Enter your email").subcribe-email
                button.subcribe-button(type="submit")
                  img(srcSet="./images/line.png 2x")
            .footer-column
              h4.footer-heading Services
              ul.footer-links
                each val in ["Trip Planner", "Tour Planning", "Tour Guide", "Tour Package", "Tour advice"]
                  li.footer-item
                    a.footer-link(href="#")= val
            .footer-column
              h4.footer-heading Support
              ul.footer-links
                each val in ["Account", "Legal", "Contact", "Terms & Condition", "Privacy Policy"]
                  li.footer-item
                    a.footer-link(href="#")= val
            .footer-column  
              h4.footer-heading Business
              ul.footer-links
                each val in ["Success", "About Locato", "Blog", "Information", "Travel Guide"]
                  li.footer-item
                    a.footer-link(href="#")= val
